com.ibm.team.workitem.common.model
Interface IDeliverable

All Superinterfaces:
IAuditable, IAuditableHandle, IDeliverableHandle, IItem, IItemHandle, IManagedItem, IManagedItemHandle, IProjectScoped
public interface IDeliverable
extends IDeliverableHandle, IAuditable, IProjectScoped

A deliverable represents a release like a milestone or final release. Deliverables are scoped to a project area.

Since:
0.6
